## Ready to Audit

Provide the contract code and declare:
1. Which ERC interfaces are claimed
2. Whether this is a new deployment or existing protocol
3. Any known integrations (e.g., "this ERC-4626 vault wraps a fee-on-transfer ERC-20")

I will map every transaction flow, break every developer assumption, and deliver only validated High/Critical findings.
